ead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後亦試過好多次 突然一瞬間好掛住佢 我部手機唔夠5秒就起到響佢打黎<br />\n我每次鐘意第個 想試下一齊(佢永遠會好岩時間出現提醒我佢既存在)<br />\n佢落仔都係我陪佢去落<br />\n之後起3年前同佢傾過 想同返佢一齊....佢果陣叫我去外國陪佢過聖誕(去左外國讀書)<br />\n最後我都係冇去到 曾經因為一個前度同佢嘈到絕交之後都係搵返大家<br />\n到岩岩半年前傾過 大家都強調係朋友 雖然唔知點解咁強調 但問心 大家都係最依賴最信賴大家 大家心底依然都係最重要果個"},{"pid":"015b480ab5615d214575aada07e718b8901adec5","tid":734852,"uid":190705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:36:40.000Z","msg":"打完醒起佢都係絲打.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef596b22b03f2f308c3695171c1f709124f1f7d3","tid":734852,"uid":182134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fdb71426fac632297af98efc3b14b8e150e7b8e","tid":734852,"uid":155130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cec366e724ec5ed6f153b53c5f89d3c3f34f1631","tid":734852,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9767d9df8f14cc6ab8649eff69ac7ac39801fa6","tid":734852,"uid":155130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇依個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"暫時未搵到人代替到佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"同意 亦代替唔到佢 幾年都仲係成日諗起佢 特別係依家大家都講過對大家仲有感覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"點樣同大家講<br />\n但又唔可以一齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時機唔啱所以分手<br />\n有contact既時候佢明明關心我<br />\n但話唔可以一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be87af76646ec2f8c66c0fcc48839b951cc8abfb","tid":734852,"uid":193969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"細個小學有個同學係課外活動識，之後發現原來佢只係住我隔離果座。上到中學都其實有keep住聯絡，不過真係冇乜見面。真到我大學有年暑假返左香港跟住去表白結果俾佢好人咭咗。事後我發現原來係我表白前一排佢就同人岩岩開始咗(係好短時間之前)佢男朋友仲係我大學圈子裡一位同學既細佬。<br />\n可能就係差果小小時間，我知道如果我早啲...甚至早一兩年結果可能就會唔同。<br />\n其實已經過左都好多年，但係只能怪自己當時唔識捉緊個機會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749724146f9d2a20467b442450bc9055e8c6a6d0","tid":734852,"uid":155130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015b480ab5615d214575aada07e718b8901adec5","tid":734852,"uid":190705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:36:40.000Z","msg":"打完醒起佢都係絲打.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"我諗緊回點解講啲野咁怪 我以為巴打來"},{"pid":"47f3181ac0f0e29d7501441291c264e14faa5e1c","tid":734852,"uid":155130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5bc1431a121ff64ad23ee4dc602ec204f10c24f","tid":734852,"uid":162490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n兜兜轉轉最後互相block咗大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"佢block左隔一排又解番 唔知咩心態"},{"pid":"b7590b97be09585fc4f01177efd8aa71a1523416","tid":734852,"uid":155130,"like":1,"disli